  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dill Sterling, the main character, will have to solve the mystery of astrotesters disappearance. Find preserved relics and become one of those, who will save his own planet from destruction.   </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Thoughtfully designed levels with a connected storyline.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411370/extras/61e7138c4445b1f334037f6c579a925a.poster.avif?t=1769666560\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411370/extras/61e7138c4445b1f334037f6c579a925a.webm?t=1769666560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique enemy AI for each type, including mini bosses<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411370/extras/708645ff7831b114f2aee10582494aaa.poster.avif?t=1769666560\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411370/extras/708645ff7831b114f2aee10582494aaa.webm?t=1769666560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple gameplay mechanics: vehicle control (story-driven), puzzles, cooperation with NPCs and more.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411370/extras/4d2e1b6da544c13c975a221fbdcb57cf.poster.avif?t=1769666560\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411370/extras/4d2e1b6da544c13c975a221fbdcb57cf.webm?t=1769666560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411370/extras/4d2e1b6da544c13c975a221fbdcb57cf.mp4?t=1769666560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engaging characters and dialogues.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411370/extras/08105d62075a2a9c69645c2e34030866.poster.avif?t=1769666560\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411370/extras/08105d62075a2a9c69645c2e34030866.webm?t=1769666560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
